lamco-rdp-server (1.4.3-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * feat: Add static password authentication with multi-user support
  * feat: Add IPv6 listen address support
  * feat: Add Portal host app identity registration for KDE compatibility
  * fix: Restore KDE clipboard sync via data-control/wl-clipboard provider
  * fix: Cache RDP clipboard text for data-control backends
  * fix: Route CJK input via Portal keysym injection for BMP characters
  * fix: Pause Klipper cooperation sync during CJK clipboard-paste fallback
    - Prevents "已复制" toast spam during Chinese/Japanese/Korean typing
    - Preserves original clipboard content after CJK paste operations
    - Shares cjk_paste_paused flag between input handler and ClipboardOrchestrator
